             was indicted for <rs id="t18010520-75-off411" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18010520-75-off411" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010520-75-off411" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18010520-75-cd412" type="crimeDate">15th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010520-75-off411 t18010520-75-cd412"></join>, ten shawls, value 24s. 6d. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18010520-75-victim584" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        West
                     <interp inst="t18010520-75-victim584" type="surname" value="West"></interp>
